    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "active_lock_reason": null,
    "body": "As we worked through (at some length) in https://github.com/emberjs/guides/issues/1185 having multiple versions of the guides in search engine indices ends up diluting our ability to actually find **anything** using Google search.  It's not an ideal situation.  We'd been pending adding canonical urls to our old versions of the guides while we worked on adding better search to those versions of the guides, but that work has hit some snags (see https://github.com/emberjs/guides/pull/1750 for an example).  Rather than have that block us indefinitely, I'm starting in on adding canonical urls.  Help here would be much appreciated.\r\n\r\nWe need to do two things to get this work done.\r\n\r\nFirst, we need to add the canonical url to the appropriate branch of the guides (see https://github.com/emberjs/guides/commit/60573df63f2d00590b0d9ca80cac402c3921d6b0 for an example) and send in a PR with the change to the appropriate branch:\r\n\r\n- [x] 1.10\r\n- [x] 1.11 (https://github.com/emberjs/guides/pull/1817)\r\n- [ ] 1.12 (copy the PR to 1.11)\r\n- [ ] 1.13 (copy the PR to 1.11)\r\n- [ ] 2.0 (copy the PR to 1.11)\r\n- [ ] 2.1 (copy the PR to 1.11)\r\n- [ ] 2.2\r\n- [x] 2.3\r\n- [x] 2.4\r\n- [x] 2.5\r\n- [ ] 2.6\r\n- [ ] 2.7\r\n- [ ] 2.8\r\n- [ ] 2.9\r\n- [ ] 2.10\r\n- [ ] master\r\n\r\nSecond (this is the harder part), we need to send in the built version of the guides to the https://github.com/emberjs/guides.emberjs.com repo.  To do this, you'll need to do the following steps:\r\n\r\n1. `bundle exec middleman build` in your updated `guides` repo\r\n2. replace the `snapshots/<version>` folder in the `guides.emberjs.com` repo with the new `build` folder in your `guides` repo\r\n3. run `node task/update-version.js <version>` in the root of the `guides.emberjs.com` repo to update some necessary places in your new built files\r\n4. send in a PR\r\n\r\nThese are the versions that still need to be updated:\r\n- [x] 1.10 (https://github.com/emberjs/guides.emberjs.com/pull/34)\r\n- [x] 1.11 (https://github.com/emberjs/guides.emberjs.com/pull/35)\r\n- [ ] 1.12 (PR should look similar to v1.11)\r\n- [ ] 1.13\r\n- [ ] 2.0\r\n- [ ] 2.1\r\n- [ ] 2.2\r\n- [x] 2.3 (https://github.com/emberjs/guides.emberjs.com/pull/33)\r\n- [x] 2.4 (https://github.com/emberjs/guides.emberjs.com/pull/33)\r\n- [x] 2.5 (https://github.com/emberjs/guides.emberjs.com/pull/33)\r\n- [ ] 2.6\r\n- [ ] 2.7\r\n- [ ] 2.8\r\n- [ ] 2.9\r\n- [ ] 2.10",
